HEADWORD: Lanky
<hw>Lank"y</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Somewhat lank; tall, thin, bony and
ungraceful.</def> <rj><au>Thackeray.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>lanky</qex> Dinka, nearly seven feet in height.</q>
